insert into periodic_exam_school_qst_result(school_id,exam_code,exam_date,grade,total_marks,obtained_marks,indicator,indicator_id ,academic_year,students_attended,subject,school_name,cluster_id,cluster_name,total_students, block_id,block_name,district_id,district_name,created_on,updated_on)
select data.school_id,data.exam_code,data.exam_date,data.grade,data.total_marks,data.obtained_marks,data.indicator,data.indicator_id ,date_part('year', data.exam_date) as academic_year,e.students_attended, d.subject_name as subject,b.school_name,b.cluster_id,b.cluster_name,c.students_count, b.block_id,b.block_name,b.district_id,b.district_name, now(),now() from (select data.* from (select a.school_id,a.exam_code,to_date(substr(a.exam_code,8,14)::text, 'DDMMYYYY')as exam_date,a.studying_class as grade,b.indicator_id,b.indicator, b.question_marks*sum(students_attended) as total_marks,sum(a.obtained_marks)as obtained_marks,b.exam_id from (select exam_id,school_id,exam_code,studying_class,question_id,sum(obtained_marks)as obtained_marks,count(distinct(student_uid)) as students_attended from periodic_exam_result_trans group by exam_id,school_id,exam_code,studying_class,question_id)as a left join (select exam_id,indicator_id,indicator,question_marks from periodic_exam_qst_mst group by exam_id,indicator_id,indicator,question_marks) as b on a.exam_id=b.exam_id and a.question_id=b.indicator_id group by a.school_id,a.exam_code,a.studying_class,b.indicator_id,b.indicator,b.exam_id,b.question_marks,a.question_id)as data where data.total_marks is not null)as data inner join (select a.school_id,a.school_name,b.school_latitude,b.school_longitude,a.cluster_id,a.cluster_name,b.cluster_latitude,b.cluster_longitude, a.block_id,a.block_name,b.block_latitude,b.block_longitude,a.district_id,a.district_name,b.district_latitude,b.district_longitude from school_hierarchy_details as a inner join school_geo_master as b on a.school_id=b.school_id where a.school_name is not null and a.cluster_name is not null and b.school_latitude>0 and b.school_longitude>0 and b.cluster_latitude>0 and b.cluster_longitude>0 )as b on data.school_id=b.school_id left join (select school_id,count(distinct(student_uid)) as students_count from periodic_exam_result_trans group by school_id)as c on data.school_id=c.school_id left join (select exam_id,assessment_year,exam_code,subject_name from periodic_exam_mst) as d on data.exam_id=d.exam_id and data.exam_code=d.exam_code left join (select exam_code,exam_id,question_id,school_id,studying_class,count(distinct(student_uid)) as students_attended from periodic_exam_result_trans group by exam_code,exam_id,question_id,school_id,studying_class) as e on data.school_id=e.school_id and data.grade=e.studying_class and data.exam_code=e.exam_code and data.indicator_id=e.question_id where total_marks>=obtained_marks on conflict(school_id,exam_code,academic_year,indicator_id) do update set school_id=excluded.school_id,exam_code=excluded.exam_code,exam_date=excluded.exam_date,grade=excluded.grade,total_marks=excluded.total_marks, obtained_marks=excluded.obtained_marks,indicator=excluded.indicator,indicator_id=excluded.indicator_id,academic_year=excluded.academic_year,subject=excluded.subject, students_attended=excluded.students_attended,school_name=excluded.school_name,total_students=excluded.total_students, cluster_id=excluded.cluster_id,cluster_name=excluded.cluster_name,block_id=excluded.block_id,block_name=excluded.block_name, district_id=excluded.district_id,district_name=excluded.district_name,updated_on=now()
